        <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-8 mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Rescue & Modernize</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
          Revive slow or outdated Rails applications. Update to modern Rails, fix performance issues, eliminate technical debt, and reduce hosting costs. Your app will feel brand new.
